com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.util
Class FilterList

java.lang.Object
  com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.util.FilterList

public final class FilterList
extends java.lang.Object

A filtered view on the elements of another list.

The view is mutable, supporting addition and removal of elements.
